Signed-off-by: Andrii Nakryiko <andrii@kernel.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/bpf/1649299098-2069-1-git-send-email-baihaowen@meizu.com
Acked-by: Shung-Hsi Yu <shung-hsi.yu@suse.com>
---
 tools/lib/bpf/usdt.c |    4 ++--
